event.description:
Let’s celebrate our 10 years Anniversary Party with
French Wines, Cheeses and R&B, Soul, Hip-Hop, Ｊａｚｚ & Funk live songs

Join our all-you-can-drink Soul and live-song event with 7 kinds of French wines.

Savor our different types of cheese as well as our freshly baked baguettes.

David Whitaker, the talented American singer, will perform R&B, Soul, Jazz and Funk songs.
Place: Fiat Space, Aoyama

Prices: Normal ticket: 3980yen, VIP ticket: 4980yen

Advance reservation at least 7 days before!
